---
import Container from '../Container.astro';
import Button from '../Button.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-20">
  <Container>

<div class="mb-16 text-center">
  <p class="section-label mb-4">Journey x Philosophy</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground md:text-5xl">
    Listen. Build. Iterate.
  </h2>

  <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
    Over the last decade I've worked across technology, operations, strategy and startups — in a world where the ability to build was a competitive advantage.
  </p>
  <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
Today, what fascinates me most is distribution. When AI makes it easier than ever to create products, how do you get people to discover, trust and adopt them?
  </p>
</div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-2">

      <!-- Personal -->
      <div class="card p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">
          Professional Journey
        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          I studied Electrical Engineering at IIT Madras before heading to
          IIM Lucknow for an MBA.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          Since then I've worked across Citi, Olam and Katha Ads —
          moving between technology, operations, product and business strategy.
        </p>

      </div>

      <!-- Philosophy -->
      <div class="card p-8">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground">
          Product Philosophy
        </h3>

        <p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          I believe the best products are built close to the user.
          The more conversations you have, the more assumptions get challenged.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
          I enjoy understanding how people make decisions, what motivates
          them to act, and how products can create value at scale.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <Button href="/about" variant="secondary">
        Read my full story
      </Button>
    </div>

  </Container>
</section>

